        "name": "Bone Slam (Physical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Necropede slams its skeletal body onto a target, dealing D6 Bludgeoning damage.</p></div>"
      },
      {
        "startDie": 3,
        "endDie": 4,
        "name": "Soul Drain (Magical)",
        "description": "<div><p>The Necropede emits a burst of its dark aura, attempting to drain the life force of a target. The target must succeed on an Endurance check or take 2D4 Necrotic damage and the Necropede gains Temporary Health equal to half the damage dealt.</p></div>"
